io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.salesmanagement.service.impl.rest

Class SalesmanagementRestServiceTestHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.salesmanagement.service.impl.rest.SalesmanagementRestServiceTestHelper

  • public class SalesmanagementRestServiceTestHelper
extends Object
    This is a helper class for the classes SalesmanagementRestServiceTest and SalesmanagementHttpRestServiceTest. It capsulates some sample attributes as constants used both testing classes. Moreover it provides two methods to create sample OrderCto and OrderPositionEto objects using the sample attributes defined by this class.
